Components
1. Core
Location: /lib/core
Description: Contains:
             - shared functionality across the application
             - dependency injection
             - network manager
             - preferences
             - routing
             - app style
             - app constants
             - ui components
             - error handling
             - base use cases

2. Features
Location: /lib/features
Description:

* Feature: Auth

Data layer:
Location: /lib/features/user/data
Description: Contains data models and repository implementations.

Domain layer:
Location: /lib/features/user/domain
Description: Contains entities, repository interfaces, and use cases.

Presentation layer:
Location: /lib/features/user/presentation
Description: Contains UI-related components, including BLoC (Business Logic Component), pages, and widgets.